am\": \"a needle\", \"from\": 447, \"to\": 455}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 games\", \"from\": 469, \"to\": 483}, {\"ngram\": \"inParis\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 491}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Britishsculptor DrWillard Wigan, who has created the world's smallest handmade micro-art, meticulously crafted a miniature version of the Olympic mascot, Phryge, in a feat which involved holding his breath, working between heartbeats and using his pulse as a jackhammer.\", \"from\": 495, \"to\": 765, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 521, \"end\": 526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wigan\", \"score\": 0.8699334199781571, \"rank\": 0.09036401466217502, \"text\": \"Wigan\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wigan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wigan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world's smallest handmade micro\", \"from\": 544, \"to\": 579}, {\"ngram\": \"art\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 583}, {\"ngram\": \"a miniature version\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 625}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic mascot\", \"from\": 629, \"to\": 647}, {\"ngram\": \"Phryge\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 655}, {\"ngram\": \"a feat\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 666}, {\"ngram\": \"his breath\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 700}, {\"ngram\": \"heartbeats\", \"from\": 718, \"to\": 728}, {\"ngram\": \"his pulse\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 748}, {\"ngram\": \"a jackhammer\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The handmade microscopic version of the official mascot, the smallest in Olympic history, can be seen holding a medal which was crafted from 24-carat gold and is roughly the size of a blood cell.\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 962, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The handmade microscopic version\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 799}, {\"ngram\": \"the official mascot\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 822}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic history\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 855}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 884}, {\"ngram\": \"24-carat gold\", \"from\": 908,